Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.77,0:01:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You're looking tan and rested.\NHawaii agrees with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.40,0:01:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It was fun! Let's all go\Ntogether next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.44,0:01:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.74,0:02:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't last.\NNot at this price.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.50,0:02:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.39,0:03:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.05,0:03:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.27,0:04:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.63,0:05:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.92,0:05:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Adelstein is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.44,0:05:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Hitoshi Ishida.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.99,0:05:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Koichi Tanaka's right hand
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.78,0:05:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and de facto head of\Nthe Chihara-kai crime family.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.43,0:05:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.74,0:06:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.63,0:06:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I speak Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.30,0:09:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.97,0:10:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You're into Backstreet?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.34,0:13:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'll bring some home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.26,0:13:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise. I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.97,0:13:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,All right... I'm hanging up.\NBye.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.25,0:15:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Kurihira! Shinohara!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.38,0:15:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to the legal bureau\Nand pull the company's address,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.38,0:15:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,CEO's name,\Nanything you can get.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.95,0:15:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooo, mysterious.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.79,0:15:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Not mysterious.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.25,0:16:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.25,0:16:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Call me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.75,0:16:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.47,0:16:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.68,0:16:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- See you tomorrow.\N- Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.14,0:17:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,She was...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.56,0:17:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,so full of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.57,0:17:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We understand she was\Nin quite a lot of debt,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.03,0:17:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,that she had fallen behind\Nin her payments.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.66,0:17:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So then...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.79,0:17:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyon-suk deserved to die...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.33,0:17:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,because she owed money\Nand couldn't pay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.04,0:17:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.42,0:17:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,My colleague\Nmeant no disrespect.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.47,0:17:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We want to find the people\Nwho pressured your wife
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.68,0:17:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and hold them accountable.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.56,0:17:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you Korean too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.14,0:17:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,My grandparents\Nare from Jinhae.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.48,0:17:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Jinhae...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.27,0:17:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The cherry blossoms there\Nare famous.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.53,0:17:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. They are beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.32,0:18:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,My wife was from Jinhae.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.66,0:18:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We used to go all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.92,0:18:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.26,0:18:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Those guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.80,0:18:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,they came to our home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.85,0:18:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,In Japanese, if you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.52,0:18:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,They...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.56,0:18:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,went to the beauty parlor\Nwhere she worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.69,0:18:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,She was so ashamed...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.66,0:18:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,and afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.04,0:18:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait here a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.98,0:19:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,A collection letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.31,0:19:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It came a week after Hyon-suk\Nkilled herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.78,0:19:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Even then...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.11,0:19:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,those bastards\Nwouldn't leave her alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.00,0:19:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.75,0:19:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And we are\Nvery sorry for your loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.96,0:19:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.31,0:19:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Oyabun, Tozawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.31,0:19:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,is spreading a bogus rumor
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.90,0:19:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,that Ishida is connected\Nto the police,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.61,0:20:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,in order to divide and\Ndestabilize the Chihara-kai.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.74,0:20:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Ishida won't take it\Nlying down,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.49,0:20:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and then we'll have a war\Non our hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.70,0:20:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't let that happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.08,0:20:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,A rumor like that\Nwouldn't carry much weight
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.71,0:20:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,coming from Ishida's enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.04,0:20:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But if it came from inside\Nthe Chihara-kai itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.92,0:20:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,that's another story.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.01,0:20:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Meaning your clever boss\Nhas managed to flip someone
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.72,0:20:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,in Ishida's camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.73,0:20:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So, who's the mole?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.98,0:20:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know\Nwhat you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.96,0:20:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You're free to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.96,0:20:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.63,0:21:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You release me now, my crew\Nwill think I cut a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.09,0:21:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not bad.\NIt would be interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.26,0:21:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you mind? We need the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.80,0:21:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll kill me!\NYou know it--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.18,0:21:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The mole. Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.03,0:22:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That gaijin hostess you have\Na hard-on for?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.03,0:22:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Duke says she's looking\Nto open up another club.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.29,0:22:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Go talk to her. Make sure\Nshe knows... Everybody pays.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.66,0:22:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Scare her a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.88,0:22:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.38,0:22:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, fuck her all you want,\NI don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.05,0:22:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I see a future for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.92,0:22:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't blow it\Nover some piece of ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.27,0:22:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the popular one, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.98,0:22:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah. That's the one.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.89,0:22:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it good?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.15,0:22:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really spacious\Nand nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.94,0:22:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go together next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.91,0:22:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I've gone to the big banks\Nand the other loan companies.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.33,0:23:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No one else will lend to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.09,0:23:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm desperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.80,0:23:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,My husband gambles away\Nhis paycheck every month.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.64,0:23:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing left\Nto pay the bills.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.69,0:23:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.53,0:23:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You've come to the right place.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.12,0:23:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't turn anyone away.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.96,0:23:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just need you to sign some\Npapers before we get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.79,0:23:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.20,0:25:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Get the map.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.66,0:25:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Map, map, map!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.43,0:26:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's check.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.44,0:26:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.29,0:26:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the home\Nof Kyoshi Sonoda?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.01,0:26:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Would it be possible to speak\Nto him?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.51,0:26:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,To my father?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.43,0:26:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.26,0:26:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,but my father has been unable\Nto see guests for years.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.85,0:27:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Samantha-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.18,0:27:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I got my revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.55,0:31:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Meicho Shimbun, City Desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.34,0:31:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Detective Toma, thank you\Nfor returning my call.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.22,0:31:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering\Nwhen you might be free.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.22,0:31:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,As the girl said,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.81,0:31:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you about those\Nwho are overly nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.11,0:31:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And the girl placed her hands\Non the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.73,0:31:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,She asked, who is white,\Nfluffy, tasty,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.82,0:31:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,and smarter than a wolf?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.49,0:31:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That is me, she said.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.04,0:32:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And she closed the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.42,0:32:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The end.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.04,0:32:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it. Let's sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.04,0:32:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Read some more!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.75,0:32:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to sleep.\NShino, let's go to your bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.92,0:32:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Then do the song!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.59,0:32:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Frog song, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.01,0:32:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah. Right. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.81,0:32:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,One second.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.23,0:32:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The frog's song...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.44,0:32:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We can hear it...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.90,0:32:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Gwa, gwa, gwa, gwa...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.36,0:32:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Gero, gero, gero, gero,\Ngwa, gwa, gwa.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.25,0:32:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming in!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.72,0:33:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you you'd regret\Nit if you fucked with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.98,0:33:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.40,0:33:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.78,0:35:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's what I don't get,\Nthough.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.54,0:35:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I do manage to get\Nsomething from my source...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.04,0:35:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,how's your boss\Nsupposed to know
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.42,0:35:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,the information's any good?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.38,0:35:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Because if it isn't,\Nwe'll come after you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.95,0:36:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.84,0:36:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, I'll have\Nsome too. Just a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.05,0:36:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be sipping mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.10,0:36:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Once again, to Emi-chan.\NKanpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.15,0:36:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,To Emi-chan. Kanpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.73,0:36:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,How many times\Nare we toasting?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.86,0:36:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the fourth.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.61,0:36:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You're looking good.\NYou got a boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.57,0:36:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet you got a lot\Nof boyfriends.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.87,0:36:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I was hoping you could take\Na look at something for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.25,0:36:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.92,0:36:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,- Oh, yeah, I remember her.\N- She was cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.17,0:37:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,If you like that type.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.67,0:37:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It happened\Njust recently, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.30,0:37:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.55,0:37:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But when I read\Nthe confession--
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.18,0:37:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, I'm confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.68,0:37:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you get ahold\Nof the confession?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.89,0:37:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm. How did I?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.81,0:37:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Thatta girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.39,0:37:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Got her trained, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.19,0:37:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,How's your daughter,\NDetective Toma? Sixteen now?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.53,0:37:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,She must be so proud of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.28,0:37:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,In the confession, the suspect\Nclaims he smashed her head in.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.83,0:37:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.46,0:37:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Does she look like her head\Nwas smashed in?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.13,0:37:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,She was strangled.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.34,0:37:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoever actually killed her\Nwould know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.72,0:37:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, this guy confessed.\NOf his own accord.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.85,0:37:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Case closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.23,0:37:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but--
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.35,0:37:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's always work with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.73,0:37:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, loosen up.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.98,0:38:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get another round!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.90,0:38:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.26,0:39:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.42,0:40:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I like how you dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.05,0:40:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.79,0:42:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone has ordered
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.45,0:42:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,a bottle of Camus Tradition\Nfor 1.2 million yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.62,0:43:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Whichever.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.58,0:43:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,There are so many options.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.96,0:43:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,This one?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.09,0:43:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- I can't pick.\N- Oh, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.50,0:43:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's pick this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.34,0:44:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.93,0:44:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What were you watching?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.81,0:44:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuka-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.64,0:44:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch me, and only me.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.58,0:46:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Could we see\Neach other again sometime?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.50,0:46:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.84,0:46:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.22,0:46:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.10,0:46:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.56,0:47:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.65,0:47:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Call me anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.05,0:47:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Burning the midnight oil?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.76,0:47:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Or avoiding going home?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.52,0:47:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Chasing a story.\NIt's still out of reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.98,0:47:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep after it. I'm confident\Nit won't elude you for long.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.78,0:47:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.36,0:47:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish my colleagues shared\Nyour confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.58,0:48:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,When in doubt,\Nfollow your instinct.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.42,0:48:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what anyone\Nhere says. It's worked for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.63,0:48:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Always.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.34,0:48:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Always?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.43,0:48:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I hired you, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.85,0:48:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.35,0:48:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night to you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.89,0:48:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome, Mr. Sato.\NPlease follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.79,0:48:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's your Peking duck.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.34,0:48:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,America is big.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.57,0:49:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- I know.\N- Very Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.29,0:50:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.36,0:51:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.49,0:51:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Vacheron Constantin, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.45,0:51:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a good eye...\Nfor a gaijin.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.74,0:51:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You have good taste...\Nfor a gangster.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.91,0:51:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Who do you think\Nyou're talking to?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.37,0:51:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Please relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.14,0:51:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,If you ever wanna talk shop...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.35,0:51:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Whenever.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.31,0:51:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Reporters here\Nare not always well liked.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.65,0:51:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Soon you will find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.19,0:51:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially if they're good\Nat their job.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.61,0:52:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So good reporters here\Nhave a lot of enemies?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.40,0:52:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,A man without enemies\Nis no man at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.91,0:52:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Give my respects\Nto your oyabun.
